articles.author: Dan Sheldon
articles.title: Manchester United record £6.3m profit in quarterly accounts - The Athletic
articles.description:
Manchester United recorded a £6.3million profit for the three months ended December 2022, while also seeing their commercial revenue rise £14.3m to £78.7m in the same quarter.
Match day revenue, however, fell £4.7m to £29.9m due to playing two less home games…
